title: Smelling Perfumes While on Day Hike Rest, Setting Up
description: A compound laugh beginning with a belly laugh and trailing to a chuckle. Ella was taking a rest with a dear friend on a long walk in Wilderness Park and brought samples of natural, wild-crafted perfumes for the pair to smell and describe the scents of together. This is the first laugh in a series of three clips isolating distinct laughs from the original recording. This laugh occured while setting up the recording. Ella remembers feeling amusing, silly, and charmed.
subject: amusing;belly laugh;charmed;chuckle;compound laugh;pair;silly
creator: Durham, Ella
